How has Tamil cinema changed in the way it deals with liquor? And what role has Prohibition played in this? The Hindu explores...
Updated: May 12, 2016 17:49 IST
From pre-Independence period till today, how has cinema portrayed drinking of alcohol.
The Hindu 's Preethi Ramamoorthy and Sruthi Radhakrishnan find out what has changed over the years.
